_:ef7ad581131011a264401d43d0eece97 a <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E52_Time-span> ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "He was a saintly monk of  the spiritual line of ʾabbā \n                  ʾAnorewos \"the Elder\" in the 15th century. \n                  He was born from  his father ʾAmmǝḫa Ṣǝyon who was the head of the \n                  royal army and Zarʾa ʾAbrǝham was raised to be a soldier \n                  and assumed his father's position after the later death. However, he left his military role and became a warrior for God." .
